<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Your Password - ATC Africa</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #1f1f1f;
        background-color: #f6f7f9;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #e6e7eb;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #4b0082;
        padding: 32px 28px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #3e006e;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .header p {
        font-size: 14px;
        opacity: 0.9;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 28px;
      }

      .security-notice {
        background-color: #fff8e5;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        border-left: 4px solid #b68b00;
      }

      .security-notice h3 {
        color: #6a4e00;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .security-notice p {
        color: #6a4e00;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .reset-message {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .reset-message h2 {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .reset-message p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }

      .reset-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4b0082;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin: 16px 0;
        text-align: center;
        min-width: 200px;
      }

      .reset-button:hover {
        background-color: #3e006e;
      }

      .manual-link {
        background-color: #f7f8fc;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
        word-break: break-all;
      }

      .manual-link h3 {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .manual-link a {
        color: #4b0082;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        font-size: 13px;
        background-color: #f6f7f9;
        padding: 8px 10px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 4px;
      }

      .expiry-notice {
        background-color: #fdecee;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 14px;
        margin: 16px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #c51f2f;
      }

      .expiry-notice p {
        color: #8e1220;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .help-section {
        background-color: #f7f8fc;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 16px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #4b0082;
      }

      .help-section h3 {
        color: #1f1f1f;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .help-section ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding-left: 0;
      }

      .help-section li {
        padding: 5px 0;
        color: #333;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 18px;
      }

      .help-section li:before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 11px;
        width: 6px;
        height: 6px;
        background-color: #4b0082;
        border-radius: 50%;
      }

      .footer {
        background-color: #fafbfc;
        padding: 24px 28px;
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid #eceef2;
      }

      .footer p {
        color: #566074;
        font-size: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #4b0082;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 10px;
          border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header,
        .content,
        .footer {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .reset-button {
          display: block;
          width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
        <p>Secure access to your ATC Africa account</p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="security-notice">
          <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Security Notice</h3>
          <p>
            If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email
            and contact our support team immediately.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="reset-message">
          <h2>
            Hello
            <span class="highlight"><%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></span>
          </h2>
          <p>
            We received a request to reset the password for your ATC Africa
            account. Click the button below to create a new password:
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center">
          <div class="reset-token-display">
            <p><strong>Reset Token:</strong></p>
            <div class="token-box">
              <code><%= resetToken %></code>
            </div>
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; margin-top: 10px">
              Copy this token and use it in the password reset form
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="expiry-notice">
          <p>
            <strong
              >‚è∞ This link will expire in 1 hour for security reasons.</strong
            >
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="help-section">
          <h3>Security Tips</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Choose a strong password with at least 8 characters</li>
            <li>Include a mix of uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and symbols</li>
            <li>Never share your password with anyone</li>
            <li>Use different passwords for different accounts</li>
            <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p
          style="
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 20px;
          "
        >
          Having trouble? Contact our support team for assistance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p><strong><%= companyName %></strong></p>
        <p>Connecting Africa's Tech Community</p>
        <p>üìç <a href="<%= websiteUrl %>"><%= websiteUrl %></a></p>
        <p>üìß <a href="mailto:<%= companyEmail %>"><%= companyEmail %></a></p>

        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #adb5bd">
          ¬© <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.<br />
          If you have any questions, please contact us at <%= supportEmail %>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
